{"id":282977,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/03/转载莫言两会发飙！/","date":"2013-03-09T04:15:21Z","modified":"2013-03-09T04:38:18Z","title":"莫言两会发飙！","content":"<p><strong>原文地址：</strong><a href=\"http://blog.sina.com.cn/s/blog_b3c4cb04010162hh.html\" title=\"莫言两会发飙！\">莫言两会发飙！</a><strong>作者：</strong><a href=\"http://blog.sina.com.cn/u/3016018692\" title=\"游茂名实名认证博\">游茂名实名认证博</a></p>\n<p>莫言两会一语惊人！</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/03/莫言.jpg\"><img src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/03/莫言.jpg\" alt=\"莫言\" width=\"271\" height=\"186\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-282982\" /></a></p>\n<p>莫言两会上基本不言。</p>\n<p>而今天上午却提出两个提案：</p>\n<p></p>\n<p>一、北京一定要取消暂住证制度！</p>\n<p>简直是对外地人莫大的侮辱！</p>\n<p></p>\n<p>二、取消外地人限购的政策，</p>\n<p>外地人凭啥不能在自己的首都买房？！</p>\n<p></p>\n<p>有钱凭啥不让买？！</p>\n<p>这是市场经济嘛？！</p>\n<p>这是自由平等吗？！</p>\n<p></p>\n<p>&#8212;&#8212;莫言要不不言，</p>\n<p>要不一语惊人！</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=2ea93c5b7b\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/msuvD\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":1002,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,9203],"tags":[22437,20554]}